SELECT 
        sf.sales_channel,
        sf.procured_date,
        sf.order_date,
        sf.ship_date,
        sf.delivery_date,
        sf.team_id,
        sf.customer_id,
        sf.store_id,
        sf.product_id,
        sf.order_quantity,
        sf.discount_applied,
        sf.unit_price,
        sf.unit_cost,
        cust.customer_names,
        prod.product_name,
        sl.state,
        st.team_names
FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_sales_fact sf
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers cust ON sf.customer_id = cust.customer_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products prod ON sf.product_id = prod.product_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team st ON sf.team_id = st.team_id

WITH Average_delivery_days_cte AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales
)
 SELECT 
        AVG(DATEDIFF(DAY, Order_Date, Delivery_Date)) AS Average_delivery_days
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales

WITH Average_delivery_days_cte AS (

)
 SELECT

    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales

WITH Profit_per_Customer_cte AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales
)
 SELECT 
        cust.Customer_Names,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price - Unit_Cost) * Order_Quantity * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Profit_per_customer
    FROM 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sf
    LEFT JOIN 
       PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS prod ON prod.product_id = sf.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS cust ON cust.customer_id = sf.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS sl ON sl.store_id = sf.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        cust.Customer_Names
    ORDER BY 
        Profit_per_customer DESC

WITH Revenue_Per_State AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales
)
 SELECT 
        sl.state,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Revenue_Per_State
    FROM 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales AS sf
    LEFT JOIN 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS prd ON prd.product_id = sf.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS cust ON cust.customer_id = sf.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS sl ON sl.store_id = sf.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        sl.state
    ORDER BY 
        Revenue_Per_State DESC

WITH Total_Product_Revenue_cte AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM  PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sf
)
 SELECT 
        prod.product_name,
        prod.product_id,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Total_Product_Revenue
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sf
    LEFT JOIN 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products  AS prod ON prod.product_id = sf.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
       PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team st ON st.team_id = sf.team_id
    LEFT JOIN 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS sl ON sl.store_id = sf.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        prod.product_name, prod.product_id
    ORDER BY 
        Total_Product_Revenue DESC
